# GIT-ONLY re-include. The repo-root .gitignore excludes `vendor/` (build
# artifacts), but this corpus's vendored file is a deliberate fixture — it
# exists to pin the walker's vendored-dir exclusion policy (see
# `policy_excluded` in expected-findings.yaml) and must be committed.
#
# This file is NOT read by the scanner: the sibling .relixqignore takes
# precedence in the suppression loader, so the scan-time vendored-dir policy
# is unaffected by this negation.
!vendor/
